{"tid":782020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"俾你搵咁多錢又有咩意思?","createTime":"2018-08-16T11:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T11:47:15.000Z","uid":167757,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e9520061f62caaa66b87be41e8954d898d4c1e91","tid":782020,"uid":167757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T11:17:50.000Z","msg":"細細個窮撚一個，同同學踢波對鞋着到周星馳少林足球咁都仲繼續着住一齊踢，俾人笑到習慣曬。讀書成績又差，坐自己旁邊嘅女神班長眼尾都唔望自己一下。<br />\n直到大咗之後憑藉自己努力入咗三大神科。而家做左專業人士。月收六位數字。<br />\n<br />\n但咁又點?<br />\n<br />\n自己根本一啲都唔幸福。身邊都係充斥住一班臭閪拜金港女。個閪邊比人屌撚都反曬都厚住面皮咁埋你身。<br />\n<br />\n女神班長算係自己童年最後嘅遺憾。但已經喺三年前嫁咗比個有錢佬。而家仲生埋小朋友，就算見翻都唔會有結果。<br />\n<br />\n想當年一齊踢波笑鳩自己嘅『兄弟』都係有事先搵你，無事夏迎春<br />\n<br />\n唉，到底有冇人明啊！！"},{"pid":"6fb2b0746a9c60255fe721f16167165d98e15aac","tid":782020,"uid":167757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T11:18:53.000Z","msg":"當一個城市變到咁 就算幾有錢都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdfb9adb251c5f2bf6aa3578861ec3087f1e69e8","tid":782020,"uid":80503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T11:20:06.000Z","msg":"做專業人士都咁得閒開埋d叫春post"},{"pid":"1dea25fe5b375cfdcbadd0fa0edf18651e33b5a5","tid":782020,"uid":47052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T11:21:56.000Z","msg":"你俾晒啲錢我就明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：死窮撚"},{"pid":"f20eee4ceab1eaa99c36d90d5f2909fd9a46c523","tid":782020,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T11:23:21.000Z","msg":"你自己on9姐，怪咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n窮果時唔溝女，依家就叫春，笑死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6b04ad59af8ae53740064fb4d01fb4ec48448c","tid":782020,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201